l-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>5. Fear of Anger</strong></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>â€œIf I say no, theyâ€™ll get mad.â€</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>Reality Check</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Anger â‰  danger</li>\n<li>Someone elseâ€™s anger is <strong>their responsibility</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>EI Skill</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Emotional containment</li>\n<li>Not absorbing othersâ€™ emotional reactions</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"6-fear-of-guilt\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-fear-of-guilt\" aria-label=\"6 fear of guilt permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>6. Fear of Guilt</strong></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>â€œGood people say yes.â€</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>False Guilt vs True Guilt</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>False guilt: violating someoneâ€™s expectations</li>\n<li>True guilt: violating your own values</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Key Reframe</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Saying no to whatâ€™s wrong is saying yes to whatâ€™s right</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"7-fear-of-responsibility\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#7-fear-of-responsibility\" aria-label=\"7 fear of responsibility permalink\" class=